WEBVTT

01:32.717 --> 01:34.718
Nice to meet you.
A child of the Zen'in clan,

01:34.719 --> 01:37.971
blood of Michizane, a Death Painting Womb,

01:37.972 --> 01:41.099
and the vessel of Sukuna.

01:41.100 --> 01:43.311
No greeting for me,

01:43.812 --> 01:44.728
Tengen?

01:44.729 --> 01:45.729
<i>- So this is…
- This is…</i>

01:45.730 --> 01:47.105
<i>- This person is…
- Is this a human?</i>

01:47.106 --> 01:48.399
Tengen.

01:48.983 --> 01:51.110
This isn’t our first meeting.

01:51.111 --> 01:53.112
Is it, Yuki Tsukumo?

01:53.113 --> 01:55.448
Why did you seal off
the Tombs of the Star Corridor?

01:56.449 --> 02:00.244
I was wary that you might be
in sync with Kenjaku.

02:00.245 --> 02:04.206
I cannot read the human heart.

02:04.207 --> 02:05.333
Kenjaku?

02:06.668 --> 02:08.710
Once known as Noritoshi Kamo.

02:08.711 --> 02:12.340
Now inhabiting Suguru Geto’s body.

02:12.924 --> 02:15.968
A cord of mercy, a rope of salvation…

02:15.969 --> 02:17.762
Not even ironic.

02:19.139 --> 02:21.265
Why do you look like that, Tengen?

02:21.266 --> 02:24.102
<i>This guy really chose the worst timing…</i>

02:25.103 --> 02:28.063
I am immortal, but not ageless.

02:28.064 --> 02:30.732
Live 500 years,
and you’ll look like this too.

02:30.733 --> 02:31.734
Seriously?

02:33.069 --> 02:34.612
Twelve years ago,

02:35.155 --> 02:37.406
after I failed to merge
with the Star Plasma Vessel,

02:37.407 --> 02:39.491
my aging accelerated.

02:39.492 --> 02:42.286
My individuality faded,

02:42.287 --> 02:45.373
and Heaven and Earth
became my sense of self.

02:46.416 --> 02:50.211
So, there really wasn’t
another Star Plasma Vessel?

02:51.170 --> 02:53.673
No wonder the voices never increased.

02:54.173 --> 02:55.757
Excuse me.

02:55.758 --> 02:58.385
We came to ask about Kenjaku’s objective

02:58.386 --> 03:01.179
and how to undo the Prison Realm.

03:01.180 --> 03:03.141
Could you tell us what you know?

03:05.226 --> 03:06.935
I would like to say yes,

03:06.936 --> 03:10.732
but I must set one condition.

03:11.316 --> 03:12.399
Yuta Okkotsu.

03:12.400 --> 03:13.775
Yuki Tsukumo.

03:13.776 --> 03:15.278
Death Painting Womb.

03:16.112 --> 03:19.157
Two out of the three of you
must remain here

03:19.741 --> 03:21.618
as my guards.

03:22.201 --> 03:24.662
Guards? You’re immortal, right?

03:25.246 --> 03:27.581
Are you worried about being sealed?

03:27.582 --> 03:28.917
That’s not fair.

03:29.542 --> 03:32.211
Care telling us why you need guards,
and for how long?

03:39.928 --> 03:41.054
Very well.

03:44.557 --> 03:47.017
Let us speak of Kenjaku.

03:47.018 --> 03:48.018
PURPOSE OF KENJAKU

03:48.019 --> 03:49.603
That brat's goal

03:49.604 --> 03:54.274
is the forced evolution
of humanity across all of Japan.

03:54.275 --> 03:55.442
EVOLUTION OF HUMANITY ACROSS JAPAN

03:55.443 --> 03:57.153
We’ve heard that.

03:57.820 --> 04:02.407
What exactly does he plan?
Back then, why didn't Kenjaku

04:02.408 --> 04:05.035
use your barriers and…

04:05.036 --> 04:09.456
Idle Transfiguration
to turn everyone into sorcerers?

04:09.457 --> 04:10.415
IDLE TRANSFIGURATION

04:10.416 --> 04:11.333
EVOLUTION OF HUMANITY ACROSS JAPAN

04:11.334 --> 04:15.712
He simply lacked cursed energy.

04:15.713 --> 04:19.550
Cursed energy refined through Maximum
Uzumaki cannot be returned to sorcerers.

04:20.093 --> 04:24.930
Advancing each person individually
is far too inefficient.

04:24.931 --> 04:27.766
The method he chose is assimilation

04:27.767 --> 04:30.560
between humanity and me.

04:30.561 --> 04:31.688
ASSIMILATION BETWEEN HUMANITY AND TENGEN

04:34.649 --> 04:37.192
What? But assimilation…

04:37.193 --> 04:39.444
Only Star Plasma Vessels can do that.

04:39.445 --> 04:41.280
ONLY STAR PLASMA VESSELS CAN ASSIMILATE
WITH TENGEN

04:41.281 --> 04:43.240
That was true before.

04:43.241 --> 04:44.241
DEATH OF STAR PLASMA VESSEL

04:44.242 --> 04:45.158
PREVENT ASSIMILATION OF STAR PLASMA VESSEL

04:45.159 --> 04:48.370
<i>Now that I have evolved from 12 years ago…</i>

04:48.371 --> 04:51.164
EVOLUTION OF TENGEN

04:51.165 --> 04:55.836
…assimilation with others
is not impossible.

04:55.837 --> 04:57.004
ASSIMILATION OF TENGEN AND MANKIND

04:57.005 --> 04:58.923
But there’s only one of you, right?

04:59.674 --> 05:02.509
How do you assimilate
with multiple people?

05:02.510 --> 05:07.347
Even the me standing before you now
is not truly me.

05:07.348 --> 05:11.144
My evolved soul exists everywhere.

05:11.728 --> 05:15.272
I told you before.
Heaven and Earth are my sense of self.

05:15.273 --> 05:19.401
Those who assimilate with me
will surpass even sorcerers.

05:19.402 --> 05:23.697
Present yet absent,
a new form of existence.

05:23.698 --> 05:26.158
Because I possessed barrier techniques,

05:26.159 --> 05:29.703
I retained form and reason.

05:29.704 --> 05:31.830
But if humanity evolves,

05:31.831 --> 05:35.625
and even one person gets out of control…

05:35.626 --> 05:36.585
OUT OF CONTROL

05:36.586 --> 05:37.586
The world will end.

05:37.587 --> 05:38.587
Why?

05:38.588 --> 05:41.006
There is no boundary between individuals.

05:41.007 --> 05:43.759
Malice would spread in an instant.

05:43.760 --> 05:47.137
The impurity of 100 million people
would flood the world.

05:47.138 --> 05:51.142
Tokyo would be repeated on a global scale.

05:51.851 --> 05:53.894
Why would he do that?

05:53.895 --> 05:54.811
EVOLUTION OF HUMANITY ACROSS JAPAN
REASON UNKNOWN

05:54.812 --> 05:57.355
I don’t know. I told you already.

05:57.356 --> 06:00.484
I do not understand the human heart.

06:00.485 --> 06:01.319
REASON UNKNOWN

06:01.903 --> 06:06.573
Then if you refuse,
he can't do anything, right?

06:06.574 --> 06:09.034
That is the problem.

06:09.035 --> 06:12.579
Having evolved, I am now closer to a curse

06:12.580 --> 06:15.249
than a human.

06:15.792 --> 06:16.958
I am a valid target…

06:16.959 --> 06:17.876
ACQUIRE TENGEN

06:17.877 --> 06:20.630
…for Cursed Spirit Manipulation.

06:22.423 --> 06:26.176
If Kenjaku makes contact,

06:26.177 --> 06:29.180
I may be absorbed.

06:29.764 --> 06:32.015
That is why my true body
is rejecting everything

06:32.016 --> 06:35.143
within the Tombs of the Star Corridor.

06:35.144 --> 06:37.562
And that’s why you need guards?

06:37.563 --> 06:38.647
Yes.

06:38.648 --> 06:42.025
Kenjaku is second only to me
in barrier techniques.

06:42.026 --> 06:45.530
I don’t know when this place
will be breached.

06:46.197 --> 06:47.614
Why now?

06:47.615 --> 06:50.283
He blocked the merger,

06:50.284 --> 06:53.995
then he will let you evolve,
absorb you by Cursed Spirit Manipulation,

06:53.996 --> 06:55.081
and control you.

06:55.748 --> 06:58.250
He’s tied to Sukuna…

06:58.251 --> 06:59.167
EVOLUTION OF TENGEN, ACQUIRE TENGEN

06:59.168 --> 07:01.878
…and has been a jujutsu sorcerer
for at least 1,000 years.

07:01.879 --> 07:04.257
Why act now?

07:04.966 --> 07:08.135
I, the Star Plasma Vessel…

07:08.136 --> 07:09.261
TENGEN, STAR PLASMA VESSEL, SIX EYES

07:09.262 --> 07:12.432
…and the Six Eyes are bound by causality.

07:13.641 --> 07:17.519
Kenjaku was defeated twice
by Six Eyes users.

07:17.520 --> 07:20.063
The second time, he was thorough.

07:20.064 --> 07:22.232
He killed every Star Plasma Vessel

07:22.233 --> 07:24.444
and Six Eyes user within a month of birth.

07:25.027 --> 07:29.573
<i>Yet on the day of the merger,
both appeared.</i>

07:29.574 --> 07:34.911
After that, he shifted from killing
to sealing,

07:34.912 --> 07:37.498
and sought the Prison Realm.

07:38.082 --> 07:41.585
Only one Six Eyes user exists at a time.

07:41.586 --> 07:45.213
But 12 years ago,
something unexpected happened.

07:45.214 --> 07:48.301
The intervention of Toji Zen'in.

07:48.801 --> 07:51.678
He possessed a Heavenly Restriction,
a Physical Gifted type.

07:51.679 --> 07:53.221
Among them, he was unique,

07:53.222 --> 07:56.184
a being who had completely broken free
from cursed energy.

07:58.811 --> 08:02.022
A human who stepped outside causality

08:02.023 --> 08:05.400
ended up shattering our fate.

08:05.401 --> 08:06.277
DEATH OF STAR PLASMA VESSEL

08:06.861 --> 08:10.238
<i>And there was also a boy
with Cursed Spirit Manipulation.</i>

08:10.239 --> 08:11.198
CURSED SPIRIT MANIPULATION,
DEATH OF STAR PLASMA VESSEL

08:11.199 --> 08:15.535
<i>At that point, without meaning to,
every piece fell into place.</i>

08:15.536 --> 08:17.496
<i>Six years ago,</i>

08:17.497 --> 08:21.042
<i>the Prison Realm
fell into Kenjaku’s hands.</i>

08:21.542 --> 08:25.962
Then what is the Culling Game for?

08:25.963 --> 08:28.340
Preparation before assimilation.

08:28.341 --> 08:29.591
MANKIND, TENGEN

08:29.592 --> 08:32.886
Assimilation with others is possible,

08:32.887 --> 08:36.515
but likely incomplete at present.

08:36.516 --> 08:37.474
INCOMPLETE

08:37.475 --> 08:40.685
The Culling Game uses
players’ cursed energy,

08:40.686 --> 08:43.480
the colonies, and their boundaries
to perform a ritual

08:43.481 --> 08:47.109
and sends this nation’s people
to the far shore.

08:47.652 --> 08:51.863
After that, he will begin
assimilation with me.

08:51.864 --> 08:53.532
EVOLUTION OF HUMANITY ACROSS JAPAN

08:53.533 --> 08:55.825
To sustain a ritual of this scale,

08:55.826 --> 08:59.455
Kenjaku himself must also bear
binding restrictions.

09:01.707 --> 09:03.124
RULE ADDITIONS MUST BE ALLOWED,
WITHIN REASON

09:03.125 --> 09:04.960
One condition is this.

09:04.961 --> 09:08.672
The administrator of the Culling Game
is not Kenjaku.

09:08.673 --> 09:11.675
However, this works to your disadvantage.

09:11.676 --> 09:15.638
Even if you kill Kenjaku,
the Culling Game will not end.

09:16.639 --> 09:19.099
<i>Either all players die,</i>

09:19.100 --> 09:22.769
<i>or all players refuse participation
and die.</i>

09:22.770 --> 09:25.063
<i>Until then, the Culling Game will not end.</i>

09:25.064 --> 09:28.108
<i>The rule stating perpetual continuation
exists only as insurance</i>

09:28.109 --> 09:31.820
<i>to prevent the ritual
from being interrupted.</i>

09:31.821 --> 09:33.238
Then that means…

09:33.239 --> 09:34.197
- Yes.
- Huh?

09:34.198 --> 09:35.156
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

09:35.157 --> 09:36.158
A PLAYER WHO COLLECTS 100 POINTS
MAY ADD A RULE

09:36.826 --> 09:39.244
We’ll have to participate
in the Culling Game

09:39.245 --> 09:42.414
and add a rule allowing Tsumiki

09:42.415 --> 09:44.834
and unwilling players to withdraw.

09:46.419 --> 09:49.379
At the same time, we must work
on freeing Mr. Gojo.

09:49.380 --> 09:52.382
If he’s back,
he can resolve everything himself.

09:52.383 --> 09:53.675
GOALS OF ITADORI'S GROUP

09:53.676 --> 09:56.636
ADD A RULE TO WITHDRAW FROM THE GAME
FREE SATORU GOJO

09:56.637 --> 09:58.388
Tengen…

09:58.389 --> 10:01.017
Before that, decide who will remain here.

10:02.059 --> 10:03.476
I will…

10:03.477 --> 10:04.562
stay.

10:05.896 --> 10:10.066
Yuji will need either Okkotsu
or this woman with him.

10:10.067 --> 10:11.776
Noritoshi Kamo.

10:11.777 --> 10:15.323
If Kenjaku targets Tengen here,
all the more reason.

10:16.032 --> 10:19.659
Ending his life
is salvation for my brothers.

10:19.660 --> 10:23.204
I still have more to discuss with Tengen.

10:23.205 --> 10:24.998
Is that all right, Okkotsu?

10:24.999 --> 10:28.336
Yes! I don’t want to be separated
from you guys again!

10:31.714 --> 10:32.798
Thank you.

10:34.133 --> 10:35.384
This is…

10:37.803 --> 10:40.639
the back

10:40.640 --> 10:43.683
of the Prison Realm needed to free

10:43.684 --> 10:44.684
Satoru Gojo.

10:44.685 --> 10:45.811
The back?

10:46.354 --> 10:47.812
That’s new to me.

10:47.813 --> 10:49.439
So like a back door?

10:49.440 --> 10:51.274
You could say that.

10:51.275 --> 10:53.151
Before Kenjaku found it,

10:53.152 --> 10:55.904
the Prison Realm was outside
my barrier system,

10:55.905 --> 10:58.115
most likely overseas.

10:58.741 --> 11:00.992
Sealing the back suppressed the presence

11:00.993 --> 11:04.788
of the front, but it was pointless.

11:04.789 --> 11:08.626
Satoru Gojo
is sealed inside the back as well.

11:09.627 --> 11:11.211
Then if we open this, he will be…

11:11.212 --> 11:12.379
No.

11:12.380 --> 11:16.967
Only the owner of the front,
Kenjaku, has authority.

11:17.510 --> 11:19.427
To force it open,

11:19.428 --> 11:22.514
you need either
the Inverted Spear of Heaven,

11:22.515 --> 11:24.641
which nullifies all techniques,

11:24.642 --> 11:28.229
or the Black Rope, which disrupts
and cancels technique effects.

11:28.729 --> 11:31.065
One of those is required.

11:31.690 --> 11:34.776
But the Inverted Spear of Heaven
was sealed overseas

11:34.777 --> 11:38.655
or destroyed by Satoru Gojo years ago.

11:38.656 --> 11:40.324
What was he thinking?

11:40.950 --> 11:44.869
And the Black Rope was destroyed
by Satoru Gojo last year.

11:44.870 --> 11:46.871
What's wrong with him?

11:46.872 --> 11:47.706
Right…

11:48.999 --> 11:50.542
Miguel and I searched for

11:50.543 --> 11:53.920
remaining Black Ropes in Africa, but…

11:53.921 --> 11:56.841
So, that’s why you went overseas?

11:57.425 --> 11:59.426
It turned out to be a dead end.

11:59.427 --> 12:00.885
There’s none left.

12:00.886 --> 12:02.053
What?

12:02.054 --> 12:03.972
There’s still a way, right?

12:03.973 --> 12:05.266
Yes.

12:05.850 --> 12:09.436
Among the players
in the Culling Game is a sorcerer

12:09.437 --> 12:13.314
from 1,000 years ago
who calls herself the Angel.

12:13.315 --> 12:20.072
ANGEL

12:20.698 --> 12:25.161
<i>Her technique can erase
any cursed technique.</i>

12:25.995 --> 12:28.914
HANA KURUSU

12:32.001 --> 12:32.917
PRISON REALM, SATORU GOJO,
BACK OF PRISON REALM, ANGEL

12:32.918 --> 12:36.380
- She can erase cursed techniques?
- Yes.

12:36.964 --> 12:41.051
With the Angel’s technique, the back
of the Prison Realm could be opened.

12:41.927 --> 12:44.262
Do you know where that person is now?

12:44.263 --> 12:47.057
In the eastern Tokyo colony barrier.

12:47.558 --> 12:49.851
The colony barriers reject me,

12:49.852 --> 12:52.188
so I have no further information.

12:58.068 --> 13:00.778
Let’s organize things from there.

13:00.779 --> 13:03.156
There are ten colony barriers
across the country.

13:03.157 --> 13:06.117
They are connected
to a boundary that carries

13:06.118 --> 13:08.912
Japan’s people to the beyond.

13:08.913 --> 13:12.832
<i>Crossing rivers or boundaries
to the other side</i>

13:12.833 --> 13:15.711
<i>has great meaning in jujutsu.</i>

13:16.253 --> 13:17.921
Like back at Yasohachi Bridge!

13:17.922 --> 13:18.797
THE RIVER OF YASOHACHI BRIDGE,
EQUINOX, COLONY BOUNDARIES

13:33.395 --> 13:37.440
Hokkaido isn’t included.
Is that due to the Jujutsu HQ barrier?

13:37.441 --> 13:38.608
Yes.

13:38.609 --> 13:42.529
That land has already been conditioned
as a massive spiritual site.

13:42.530 --> 13:45.032
As expected of the testing ground.

13:45.741 --> 13:48.493
<i>Crossing to the beyond sounds dramatic,</i>

13:48.494 --> 13:51.621
<i>but in truth, everyone in Japan</i>

13:51.622 --> 13:54.291
<i>is being cursed
to prepare for assimilation.</i>

13:59.171 --> 14:00.755
ACCLIMATION COMPLETE

14:00.756 --> 14:01.673
CULLING GAME

14:01.674 --> 14:04.884
How long until the ritual is complete?

14:04.885 --> 14:09.305
It depends on the Game,
but two months should be enough.

14:09.306 --> 14:10.348
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

14:10.349 --> 14:12.267
ONE MONTH FOR THE RITUAL TO BE COMPLETE

14:12.268 --> 14:15.563
It's now November 9th, 9:00 a.m.

14:16.105 --> 14:18.773
Sorcerer players began awakening around

14:18.774 --> 14:21.151
November 1st at 00:00.

14:21.652 --> 14:24.905
That gives us ten days and fifteen hours
before Tsumiki is forced

14:25.489 --> 14:27.156
to enter the Culling Game.

14:27.157 --> 14:29.117
TIME UNTIL TSUMIKI ENTERS THE CULLING GAME

14:29.118 --> 14:31.828
ADD A GENERAL RULE THAT ALLOWS PLAYERS
TO GET 100 POINTS AND LEAVE GENERAL PUBLIC

14:31.829 --> 14:32.871
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

14:32.872 --> 14:34.205
THOSE REFUSING THE ABOVE TERMS
WILL LOSE THEIR TECHNIQUE

14:34.206 --> 14:36.082
You said earlier
that refusing to participate

14:36.083 --> 14:38.419
means death, right?

14:39.003 --> 14:40.211
Yes.

14:40.212 --> 14:42.589
So technique confiscation, huh?

14:42.590 --> 14:46.135
That rule applies even to sorcerers
who join later, right?

14:47.636 --> 14:51.640
If that’s the case, it wouldn’t be done
through Idle Transfiguration.

14:52.266 --> 14:56.312
It’s confiscation, not prohibition,
so it isn’t a binding vow either.

14:57.771 --> 15:01.609
That means something is forcibly
acting on the brain, so by the rule,

15:02.151 --> 15:05.486
losing your technique equals death.

15:05.487 --> 15:08.324
Otherwise, everyone
would just refuse to participate.

15:08.908 --> 15:11.159
Your guess was spot on, Shoko.

15:11.160 --> 15:15.831
But that means for people like me,
without a technique, there is no risk.

15:16.373 --> 15:20.376
<i>I mean, what about Panda?
Does he even have a brain?</i>

15:20.377 --> 15:21.419
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

15:21.420 --> 15:22.755
PLAYERS WITH 100 POINTS CAN ADD A RULE

15:23.923 --> 15:25.173
So, what happens

15:25.174 --> 15:28.885
to regular people who were already
inside the barriers from the start?

15:28.886 --> 15:32.764
They’ll be given at least one chance
to leave.

15:32.765 --> 15:33.849
Seriously?

15:34.350 --> 15:36.143
That’s surprisingly considerate.

15:36.685 --> 15:41.314
There isn’t a rule about entering
or leaving colony barriers.

15:41.315 --> 15:42.815
Giving players a clear objective

15:42.816 --> 15:46.277
to "get out of the barrier"

15:46.278 --> 15:49.323
is likely meant to activate the game.

15:49.907 --> 15:53.952
To keep players confined,
it’s important they entered

15:53.953 --> 15:56.747
of their own free will.

15:57.247 --> 15:59.999
So that’s the give-and-take
Ino was talking about?

16:00.000 --> 16:01.042
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

16:01.043 --> 16:02.418
PLAYERS WITH 100 POINTS CAN ADD A RULE

16:02.419 --> 16:05.254
PLAYER EARNS POINTS BY TAKING
ANOTHER PLAYER'S LIFE.

16:05.255 --> 16:06.340
TAKING ANOTHER LIFE

16:08.175 --> 16:09.217
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

16:09.218 --> 16:10.635
PLAYERS WITH 100 POINTS CAN ADD A RULE

16:10.636 --> 16:12.136
POINTS ARE DETERMINED BY THE ADMINISTRATOR
AND VALUE PLACED ON THE PLAYER'S LIFE.

16:12.137 --> 16:13.972
Mixing principles into the general rules…

16:13.973 --> 16:15.223
That's so messy!

16:15.224 --> 16:16.182
SORCERER IS FIVE POINTS,
NON-SORCERER IS ONE POINT.

16:16.183 --> 16:17.267
Fushiguro?

16:17.851 --> 16:19.018
No.

16:19.019 --> 16:22.523
Tengen, what exactly is the Game Master?

16:23.232 --> 16:27.860
Each player has one <i>shikigami</i>
attached to them, which is Kogane.

16:27.861 --> 16:32.824
Strictly speaking, Kogane
isn’t the Game Master. Just the interface.

16:32.825 --> 16:33.825
KOGANE

16:33.826 --> 16:35.952
The Game Master is better thought of

16:35.953 --> 16:38.746
as the Culling Game’s program itself.

16:38.747 --> 16:40.165
I see?

16:40.666 --> 16:41.708
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

16:41.709 --> 16:43.042
PLAYERS WITH 100 POINTS CAN ADD A RULE

16:43.043 --> 16:45.004
"Adding a rule," huh…

16:45.587 --> 16:48.047
So removing existing ones isn’t an option?

16:48.048 --> 16:49.008
Well…

16:49.675 --> 16:52.469
We might be able to deny them indirectly.

16:53.178 --> 16:54.220
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

16:54.221 --> 16:55.513
PLAYERS WITH 100 POINTS CAN ADD A RULE

16:55.514 --> 16:56.431
THE GAME MASTER MUST APPROVE ANY
RULE ADDITIONS THAT AREN'T GAME-BREAKING

16:56.432 --> 16:57.850
That could work, right?

16:58.517 --> 16:59.976
Yes.

16:59.977 --> 17:01.979
The standards are too vague.

17:02.563 --> 17:03.604
No.

17:03.605 --> 17:07.150
A certain degree of fairness
can still be expected.

17:07.151 --> 17:10.570
The players have already been bound
by the general rules so far.

17:10.571 --> 17:12.363
From a jujutsu standpoint, there’s no way

17:12.364 --> 17:15.366
Kenjaku can skew things
any further in his favor.

17:15.367 --> 17:16.409
MUST ENTER THE GAME WITHIN 19 DAYS

17:16.410 --> 17:17.785
PLAYERS WITH 100 POINTS CAN ADD A RULE

17:17.786 --> 17:20.663
So we still have to keep killing people…

17:20.664 --> 17:21.622
CHANGE

17:21.623 --> 17:24.751
No. I’ve got a few ideas.

17:24.752 --> 17:25.752
IF A SORCERER DOES NOT EARN OR LOSE POINTS
WITHIN 19 DAYS, THEY LOSE THEIR TECHNIQUE

17:25.753 --> 17:27.962
CULLING GAME

17:27.963 --> 17:30.174
All right, we’ve got the information
sorted out.

17:30.674 --> 17:32.633
Now, it’s just a matter of roles.

17:32.634 --> 17:34.011
ACTION FROM NOW

17:34.762 --> 17:38.431
Yuki and Choso stay here and guard Tengen.

17:38.432 --> 17:39.348
CHOSO, YUKI TSUKUMO
GUARD TENGEN

17:39.349 --> 17:40.266
MAKI ZEN'IN

17:40.267 --> 17:43.812
I’ll head back to the Zen'in clan first
to recover cursed tools.

17:45.230 --> 17:47.398
<i>After Satoru was sealed, the cursed tools</i>

17:47.399 --> 17:51.527
<i>in Jujutsu High’s storage were taken
by the Kamo and Zen'in clans.</i>

17:51.528 --> 17:54.072
<i>But Megumi became
the head of the Zen'in clan.</i>

17:54.073 --> 17:55.281
What?

17:55.282 --> 17:56.825
I’ll explain later.

17:57.409 --> 18:00.578
Which means the Zen'in armory
is free for the taking.

18:00.579 --> 18:03.540
Before that, though, Tengen.

18:04.124 --> 18:08.294
I know. Juzo Kumiya's atelier, right?

18:08.295 --> 18:12.090
That helps a lot.
Once I’m done, I’ll look for Panda

18:12.091 --> 18:15.511
and help stabilize the Culling Game.
What about you, Yuta?

18:16.345 --> 18:20.348
I’m heading straight into a colony
to join the Culling Game.

18:20.349 --> 18:24.018
I want to gather as much information
as I can before Tsumiki

18:24.019 --> 18:25.771
and Fushiguro join.

18:26.271 --> 18:27.898
Sorry.

18:28.482 --> 18:30.942
I’ll be acting solo again,

18:30.943 --> 18:34.695
but I want to make sure no one
ends up fighting their own allies.

18:34.696 --> 18:37.657
And just in case something happens
to Tsumiki,

18:37.658 --> 18:39.701
I’ll avoid nearby colonies.

18:40.744 --> 18:43.538
Signals might be cut off inside
the barriers, so I might not be able

18:43.539 --> 18:45.791
to contact you for a while.

18:47.126 --> 18:49.836
If I switch places with Sukuna again,

18:49.837 --> 18:51.045
don’t hesitate to kill me.

18:51.046 --> 18:53.673
IF OKKOTSU STAYS NEAR ITADORI, IT'S SAFER,
BUT OKKOTSU IS MORE POWERFUL ALONE

18:53.674 --> 18:57.552
Now is not the time for that.
It will be fine.

18:57.553 --> 18:59.846
If it comes to that, after I’m dead,

18:59.847 --> 19:01.222
make sure you finish the job.

19:01.223 --> 19:04.059
No, I mean for that…

19:04.768 --> 19:05.810
Senior.

19:05.811 --> 19:07.395
Right.

19:07.396 --> 19:09.857
You two stick to the plan
and go see Kinji.

19:10.399 --> 19:11.524
Kinji?

19:11.525 --> 19:14.862
Kinji Hakari. A third-year student
who’s currently suspended.

19:15.904 --> 19:18.073
We’re short on people right now.

19:18.615 --> 19:20.242
Anyone usable gets drafted.

19:20.784 --> 19:22.202
Is he strong?

19:22.744 --> 19:27.206
He’s unpredictable, but when on a roll,
he’s stronger than me.

19:27.207 --> 19:28.792
No, he’s not.

19:31.128 --> 19:32.211
PURPOSE OF KENJAKU (TENTATIVE)

19:32.212 --> 19:33.588
ONE YEAR AGO
ACQUIRED IDLE TRANSFIGURATION

19:33.589 --> 19:34.672
12 YEARS AGO-TOJI ZEN'IN INTERVENED
TENGEN CAN ASSIMILATE WITH PEOPLE

19:34.673 --> 19:35.673
KENJAKU WILL ABSORB TENGEN
USING CURSED SPIRIT MANIPULATION.

19:35.674 --> 19:36.674
WHICH WILL ASSIMILATE ALL OF JAPAN

19:36.675 --> 19:37.758
EVOLUTION OF HUMANITY ACROSS JAPAN

19:37.759 --> 19:38.676
PURPOSE OF CULLING GAME

19:38.677 --> 19:40.178
COLONY
GENERATE CURSED ENERGY THROUGH CONFLICT

19:40.179 --> 19:41.512
MOVE PEOPLE ACROSS INTO ASSIMILATION
USING ACCUMULATED CURSED ENERGY

19:41.513 --> 19:42.638
FORCE PEOPLE ACROSS INTO ASSIMILATION
(CAST A CURSE) - ACCLIMATE

19:42.639 --> 19:43.973
ASSIMILATION BETWEEN HUMANITY AND TENGEN

19:43.974 --> 19:44.891
MISSION FOR ITADORI'S GROUP

19:44.892 --> 19:46.475
FREE SATORU GOJO
NEED ANGEL TO ASSIST

19:46.476 --> 19:48.144
SAVE TSUMIKI AND UNWILLING PLAYERS
GETS POINTS QUICKLY TO ADD A RULE

19:48.145 --> 19:49.854
MEET AT THE EAST COLONY IN TOKYO

19:49.855 --> 19:50.771
EVERYONE'S PLAN

19:50.772 --> 19:51.731
MAKI-GET CURSED TOOLS, ENTER GAME,
OKKOTSU-ENTER GAME

19:51.732 --> 19:52.732
ITADORI, FUSHIGURO-RECRUIT HAKARI
AND ENTER GAME

19:52.733 --> 19:54.109
TSUKUMO AND CHOSO-GUARD TENGEN

20:08.040 --> 20:09.208
Choso!

20:09.791 --> 20:11.376
Thanks. You really helped me out.

20:12.753 --> 20:14.129
Don’t die.

20:21.094 --> 20:23.305
- Are you crying?
- No, I’m not…

20:35.442 --> 20:36.735
Thanks.

20:38.153 --> 20:39.196
Takaba!

20:40.280 --> 20:42.365
How long are you going to be like that?

20:42.366 --> 20:45.827
Cut it out already!
You’re bringing everyone down!

20:46.787 --> 20:47.788
Yes…

20:48.830 --> 20:50.499
How old are you now?

20:51.041 --> 20:52.291
Thirty-five.

20:52.292 --> 20:54.627
Then quit already.

20:54.628 --> 20:56.921
In this business,

20:56.922 --> 20:59.590
some late bloomers suddenly hit it big

20:59.591 --> 21:01.300
for reasons nobody understands.

21:01.301 --> 21:04.178
But they don't suddenly get funny.

21:04.179 --> 21:07.224
They were always funny,
but were just buried.

21:08.350 --> 21:10.102
That’s not you.

21:10.602 --> 21:14.105
Look at Tokyo right now.
I’m telling you this for your own good.

21:14.106 --> 21:16.733
Do what you can do. Do what suits you.

21:19.736 --> 21:22.864
I don't hate your material, Takaba.

21:25.033 --> 21:26.242
Ken…

21:26.243 --> 21:28.537
Both you and that guy have it wrong.

21:29.496 --> 21:32.249
Some people get popular
even if they’re not funny.

21:36.461 --> 21:39.005
- Like a one-hit wonder?
- No.

21:39.006 --> 21:41.842
There are two kinds
who stay popular forever.

21:43.302 --> 21:45.261
Those who stay funny forever,

21:45.262 --> 21:48.515
and those who can keep believing
they’re funny forever.

21:55.480 --> 21:57.316
Which one are you?

21:58.650 --> 22:01.527
They say it’s 50-50,
but really it’s more like 70-30…

22:01.528 --> 22:04.823
They say 50-50, but… but…

22:05.449 --> 22:07.992
it’s really more like 70-30…

22:07.993 --> 22:10.912
FUMIHIKO TAKABA

23:42.337 --> 23:44.630
<i>- Hey, we're starting.
- Why did you come?</i>

23:44.631 --> 23:46.882
<i>Should I bully you like I used to?</i>

23:46.883 --> 23:47.883
<i>Maki, you do it.</i>

23:47.884 --> 23:49.218
<i>I'm you</i>

23:49.219 --> 23:51.887
<i>- and you're me.
- Make them feel glad they gave birth.</i>

23:51.888 --> 23:53.306
<i>- Yes, natural punishment
- Break…</i>

23:54.057 --> 23:55.099
All of it.

23:55.100 --> 23:55.934
NEXT EPISODE
